{"tid":1136311,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"沙維正式宣佈掛靴","createTime":"2019-05-03T02:21:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T09:38:50.000Z","uid":226925,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"fed179f7a01cd581ef07f585d9833f717e206bde","tid":1136311,"uid":226925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T02:21:02.000Z","msg":"西班牙名宿沙維周四正式宣佈掛靴，並將部署將來的教練生涯。<br />\n<br />\n效力卡塔爾球隊艾薩德體育會的39歲西班牙名宿沙維（Xavi），周四宣佈在今季結束後退出球員生涯。「這將是球員生涯最後一個球季，很期待將來擔任教練。在拉馬斯亞和告魯夫的影響下，我很久以前就有執教的念頭。」沙維說。<br />\n<br />\n沙維在巴塞隆拿出道，1998年首次在西甲上陣，合共取得17個冠軍，並協助西班牙國家隊壟斷2008至2012年的國際賽。這位中場大腦坦言最喜歡巴塞的足球，「我喜歡打進攻足球的球隊，喜歡控球在腳的足球。」<br />\n<br />\n沙維的最佳拍檔是恩尼斯達，雙方合作11個球季。他於2015年離開母會巴塞加盟艾薩德體育會，今年協助球隊獲得聯賽冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【Now Sports-體育】西班牙名宿沙...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=25410237274\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fhome%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D25410237274&d=YcIJTvf9PmU%2BR6jslv3gjD2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=5836eb44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=25410237274</a>"},{"pid":"f666fdbc352c416c884bf40a7771edf331730f5f","tid":1136311,"uid":59898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T02:24:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />xavi"},{"pid":"f81844892b121ec5a815861f179ba8cec3665e52","tid":1136311,"uid":99700,"like":6,"dislike":11,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T02:32:03.000Z","msg":"廢老"},{"pid":"78fa3fa06cf800d543b603b82cb34fcee5729f34","tid":1136311,"uid":13395,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T02:33:54.000Z","msg":"拼圖王做教練大撚鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ef96b0c1d1a45a8432dda810163e66cc4d54bf","tid":1136311,"uid":35877,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T03:00:47.000Z","msg":"Xavi做教練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}